<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Muonna lui banga ka lampi a luong in,
 Lungkhamna tui bang kinawk in;
 Bang cheng um mahleh ziehi he di'n nei hilh,
 Aphai, aphai, ka thagau ding in.

[V2]
 Aphai, ka thagau di'n,
 Aphai, aphai, ka thagau dingin.

[V3]
 2. Setan thepna leh patepna hung mahleh,
 Hetchetna pha hi vawpzing ka;
 Krista'n panpih ka ngaih zie A hezing hi,
 Ka thagau di'n A thisan A piei.

[V4]
 3. Ka gitloh-zie ngaihtuoh hi a nuom ka sai,
 Ka gitlohna cheng a bawnin;
 A Kross-ah a bawnin khetden vek ei tai,
 Ka thagau, lawpin, Lalpa pakin.

[V5]
 4. Tun chuh keia din hin Krista hi ta hen,
 Jordan tuipi kinawk mahleh;
 Thihna leh hinna ale khawksa puong ka,
 Ka thagau Na lungmuon ding ziek in.

[V6]
 5. Mahleh Lalpa, Na hung phat ding ka ngak ui,
 Ka lungtup uh van tun ahi;
 Aw, Angel Awgi leh ka Lalpa Aw chuh,
 Kinep leh chawlhna nuom, ka tha di'n.</lyrics>
<title>IT IS WELL</title>
</song>